Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,德古拉  前情提要\NPreviously on "Dracula"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你认为是谁送的？  - 你送的花啊\N- Who do you think might have sent them? - They're from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我促其进程\NI refined the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你最终会行于日下\NYou will finally be able to walk in sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,杀害  酷刑  强奸  众多屠戮\NMurder, torture, rape, wholesale slaughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是恶龙会所做的勾当\NThat is the stock and trade of the Order of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,从目前我们展示的\NFrom the moment we demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,磁技术的可能性来看\Nthe viability of geomagnetic technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会将不复存在\NNo more Order of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息  卫生局已经解除了隔离\NGreat news. The Board of Health, they've removed the quarantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你  Harker先生\NWelcome, Mr. Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我以今生起誓  我将始终以\NI swear on my life I won't ever place my own needs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,神圣的龙之会利益为上  上帝佑吾\Nabove those of this sacred Order, so help me God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,从今夜起  直至\NFrom this night and every
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们屈服  这里将会血流成河\Nnight until they yield, blood will flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson\NGrayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好好享受吧  孩子们\NBon appmotite, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Kaha Ruma  我们的猎人首领\NThis is Kaha Ruma, our leading huntsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我已经召唤了西西里人  - Loiza Scaverra？\N- I've summoned the Sicilian. - Loiza Scaverra?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要好的先知\NYou'll need a good seer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子！\NThe children!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会带走我的孩子们？\NWho in God's name would take my children?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会不知道Browning的两个孩子\NYou wouldn't happen to know anything about the disappearance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 消失的事儿吧  - 这关你什么事？\N- ...of Browning's two children? - What is it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是Grayson  对吧？\NIt was Grayson, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是他唆使你来找我的？\NGoaded you into confronting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你爱我吗？  - 别这样问我\N- Do you love me? - Don't ask me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan\NJonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jonathan  为什么？ - 因为你爱Grayson\N- Jonathan, why? - Because you love Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想行如野兽\NIf you insist on behaving like a monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我成全你\Nthen I'm going to make you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\NYou do not wanna miss this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不会想错过这个的\Nladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,未来已至\NThe future has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,今夜  伦敦市民将拥有历史性的机遇\NTonight, the citizens of London will have a historic opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(368,48)\c&H0BE7EA&\fn华文新魏\fs24}现在即未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,亲眼目睹  无线能源\Nto see for themselves the wonder of clean, wireless electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  都来吧  加入我们\NCome one, come all, join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson会…\NAlexander Grayson...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0BE7EA&\fn华文新魏\fs24\pos(390,108)}兹邀请您光临Alexander Grayson先生\N非同寻常的地磁力展示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 Van Helsing教授来这儿为您输液\NSir, Dr. Van Helsing is here to administer your infusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,把他带到地窖  我等会儿去找他\NShow him to the cellar. I'll join him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常期待看到\NI am very much looking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,明天的财经版报纸\Nforward to seeing the financial pages tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想石油价格会下滑啊\NI suspect a precipitous drop in the price of oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我期待如此\NYes. I expect so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我的直接行动\NHe's just being testy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他有点儿性急了\Nbecause I was right about direct engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没这必要  你已经坚持实施计划了\NIt wouldn't have been necessary, had you adhered to the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,计划…计划\NThe plan... the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的计划实施太长久了\NThe accursed plan was taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是因为我\NWere it not for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,共振器就不会被解禁\Nthe resonator would not have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的计划也不会回入正轨\Nbeen released and our plan now back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以Abraham\NSo, Abraham,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,为何不和我们一起共谋大事\Nwhy don't you motor to the big event with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,晚会儿吧  等我把这儿处理好\NLater, as soon as I finish here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,鄙人事务缠身\NI have much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…\NAh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还有个小事儿\NWhat about that other little problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Browning家的孩子怎么样了？\NMr. Browning's children?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你已经解决了\NI take it you've resolved that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,警方又联系你了？\NHave the police again contacted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你在报纸上看到什么了？\NHave you seen anything in the newspapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啥也没有  先生\NNot a word, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NVery well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,稍后你会过来  是吧\NYou'll be along, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会想错过\NYou wouldn't want to miss the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们强大的敌人跪倒的时刻\Nmoment we bring our greatest enemy to his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我会享受每时每刻的\NI will savor every second of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\NI assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别！关了百叶窗\NNo! Close the shutters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我头疼得厉害\NI have a shattering headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我得打电话给Hubert医生\NPerhaps I should call Dr. Hubert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不！不要找医生\NNo! No doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我就想多睡会儿\NI just need some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  妈妈  答应我…别找医生\NPlease, mama, promise me... No doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好  但如果你明天没有好展\NVery will, but I will,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我还会叫医生\Nif you haven't improved by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好  明天\NYes. Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你来干什么\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为\NI thought... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你出去了\N- I didn't think you'd be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我正准备出去\NI was... I was just on my way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把这个给你\NUm, I wanted to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不用\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是你母亲的 - 我不想要\N- It was your mother's. - I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法将它送给别人\NI could never bear to see it on anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我本以为这里某天会成为我们的家\NI thought someday this would be our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我警告过你要远离他\NI warned you to stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白\NYou don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不明白的是你  你看不出来吗\NNo, you don't understand. Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson毁了我\NGrayson's ruined me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,迫使我干些卑鄙的事\NMade me do things, vile things,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而他也将这样对你\Nand he'll do exactly the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是那样的  - 那就向我发誓\N- It's not like that. - Then swear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,以你母亲的名义向我发誓\NSwear to me on your mother's grave
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你不爱他\Nthat you don't love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你明天会去集会\NI take it you'll be at the grand demonstration?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生！\NMr. Grayson!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Grayson先生 - Grayson先生\N- Mr. Grayson! - Mr. Grayson!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎 欢迎大家\NWelcome one, welcome all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Grayson先生 - 很高兴见到您  先生\N- Mr. Grayson. - Lovely to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最终检查  正在进行\NRunning final checks. We're on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 灯光设置如何 - 同计划的一样\N- Light rigs? - Going up as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,午夜  这里一半的地方会亮如白昼\N00 P.M., and half the district will be lit up as bright as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了  Kowalski先生  太棒了\NSplendid, Mr. Kowalski. Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield先生  有Harker先生的消息吗\NMr. Renfield, any word from Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他消失两天了\NHarker? He's been missing for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,找不到他\NWe've been unable to locate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有消息了  直接带他来见我\NWhen you do locate him, bring him directly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\NI will, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,猎人们  请注意\NHuntsmen, your attention please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你们都听过传说中的先知者\NI'm sure you've all heard of our legendary seer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Loiza Scaverra\NLoiza Scaverra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,奉主之名\NIl sangue di Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,基督之血\NThe blood of Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,基督界最神圣的遗物\NThe most sacred relic in Christendom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的策略是这样的\NOur tactics are as follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,先知者会利用圣物来找到吸血鬼巢穴\NOur seer will utilize this relic to locate the nests.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们2到3人一组行动\NYou will be dispatched in teams of two or three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后发送信号给我们\NYou will then signal to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,每杀死一个发一个信号\NOne flare per kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白了吗 - 是\N- Do you understand? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那以我们救世主的信念和血起誓\NThen by the will and the blood of our savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我们将消灭吸血鬼和他的子孙\Ntoday we will annihilate the Fell One and his spawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYes!
