Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0BE7EA&\fn华文新魏\fs28\pos(372,274)}德古拉  第一季第十集\N——— 季终集 ———
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0BE7EA&\fn华文新魏\fs28\pos(360,324)}真 爱 字 幕 组\N—— 出  品 ——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我找了你两天\NI've been tryin' to contact you for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定知道Davenport大人的事吧\NYou must have heard about lord Davenport.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个混蛋…\NWhat does that bastard have to do with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker 你\NHarker, you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道发生了什么事\NI don't know what came over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝高了\NI've been drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,整件事 都记不清了\NThe whole thing, it's a blur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只知道我做了可怕的事\NExcept I've done some dreadful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很可怕的事 - Harker\N- Some terrible things. - Harker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,镇定\NPull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有人看见了吗\NDid anyone see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有 - 很好\N- No one saw. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说\NNow, you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不想被抓\NIf you don't want to get caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就什么都不要管\Nyou're gonna put everything else aside
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我\Nand trust me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗\NCan you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,首先  你要如往常一样生活\NFirst, you're gonna have to deal with things as you always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我做不到  - 你必须这样做！\N- I don't think I can. - You must!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,报社的人就在外面\NThere are press outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须把他们应付过去\Nand you have to deal with them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你往常所做的那样\Nas you've always dealt with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗\NCan you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,能\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我理解你的感受\NLook, I know how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果能把这几天应付过去\Nbut if you can get through this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你就没事了\Nyou're gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在…摆平这一切  去吧\NNow... get cleaned up. Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看到多少吸血鬼？\NHow many vampires can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,确切数字依然影影绰绰\NTotal is still in shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛暗夜中的群星  实在太多…\NAll the stars in the heavens. There are so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那好  替我找出一个\NWell, find me one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,并告诉我它在何处\Nand tell me where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,灼灼圣迹  凭彼之血\NHoly relic, through your blood
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,恶灵所隐  示于臣仆\Nshow me where the vampires are hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫Ruma  在Lower街95号\NRuma, 95 Lower Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,猎人们  出发！\NHuntsmen, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快！\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,两道猎迹  把这个告诉Jayne女士\NTwo flairs. Take this down to Lady Jayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  给您的口信\NMessage for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 具体是什么？- 一无所获\N- What is it? - Nothing of any consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你要走了？\NYou're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你看来是在这惹了麻烦\NYou seem to have matters in hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,两道绿色猎迹！Lower街95号！\NTwo green flairs! 95 Lower Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,双杀！\NTwo kills!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 出了什么事？\NSir, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡即将造访\NDeath is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander 这些 额\NAlexander, these, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这些人 他们想要… - 要什么？\N- These men, they wish... - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底想要什么？\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们…他们是泰晤士报的\NThey're... They're from The Times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想为特殊的明天拍一下…\NThey wish to photograph the resonator for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,共振器的照片\NA special feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生 您若不介意?\NMr. Grayson, if you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦泰晤士报的贵客\NThe Times of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位到来  请随意\NWelcome, gentlemen. Fire away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子犯什么病?\NWhat's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经竭尽所能了…\NLook, I'm trying the best I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,淡定点\NPull yourself together, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你  保持镇定\NI told you, stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会水到渠成\NIt'll all be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,几点了?\NTime?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,四点半\NHalf past 4:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Van Helsing在哪？\NWhere's Van Helsing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你去\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着他  我受够了\NTrack him down. I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她有点精神崩溃了\NShe's had some kind of nervous collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她已准备打包走人\NShe got a package.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Agnetta?\NAgnetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Agnetta  发生了什么？\NAgnetta, what has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他将每天送一块儿\NHe says he'll send another piece every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？ 一块什么？\NA what? Another what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你…\NYou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个杂种！\NYou bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都会因你丧命而去的！\NThey're gone because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他们给我找回来！\NYou have to find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,教授！\NProfessor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里发生了什么？\NWhat is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不过是出去了一趟  然后  我\NI just stepped outside, and then I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我就听到这巨响了\NI hear this terrible crashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对于Grayson来说我已经没用了\NI have no more use for Grayson,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  日光疫苗已经被毁\Nand now the solar vaccine has been destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson将永远无法行走于日光之下\Nand Grayson will never walk in sunlight again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是\NMuch like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Grayson先生！- Grayson先生！\N- Grayson, sir! - Mr. Grayson!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生  Grayson先生对那些声称\NMr. Grayson, Mr. Grayson, what do you say
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您的新发明不安全的人\Nto those who claim your contraption
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,您要说点什么\Nisn't safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不过是惧怕改变\NThey're afraid of change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果您对自己的发明的看法是对的\NIf you are right about your technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,您认为爱迪生对此将如何反应？\Nhow do you think Mr. Edison will react?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  介于他并未向鄙厂投资\NWell, considering he chose not to invest in my company,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,实在遗憾  我打赌\Ngravely disappointed, I'd wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一年之内我们将把那混蛋赶出这个行业\NWe'll put the scoundrel out of business by year's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真的如此？\NIs that a fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你现在应去准备准备\NPerhaps you should go prepare the demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生！ 请看这里\NMr. Grayson! Over here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生  他们说你的技术\NMr. Grayson, they say your technology
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会使上千的石油工人失去工作\Nwill put thousands of men in the petroleum industry out of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对此你有什么想对他们说的？\NWhat do you have to say to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会雇佣他们的\NI'm hiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那个谁！  他在这是干什么的？\NYou there! What's he doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  这位是Kowalski先生\NUh, gentlemen, this is Mr. Kowalski.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson的能源计划总工程师\NUh, Grayson energy's chief engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,整个工程的大脑\NThe brains behind the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让他那么做的\NI wouldn't put it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他在干嘛\NWhat's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在重启我的照相机\NI was just reloading my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得照片够多了\NI think that's enough pictures for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我看老板回来你怎么办\NSee what you can do about getting the boss back in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要做个计划的话\NI'm gonna need his help
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得需要他的帮助\Nif we're gonna make the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  这边请\NUh, gentlemen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,装好了吗？\NIs it set?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,装好了  嗯  反极性\NIt's set, all right. Inverse polarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟后等他们开启的时候…嘣\NFive minutes after they power up... boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,“嘣”是什么意思？\NWhat do you mean "Boom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是我不想在这条街\NI mean I wouldn't want to be within a street
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸的时候还呆在这\Nof this place when it goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不是只是安排一个故障吗\NIt was just supposed to malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是计划  孩子\NThis is the Order, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能手软\NWe don't take half measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson是我们的敌人\NGrayson is the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,记住了\NRemember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina\NMina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina！  Mina！\NMina! Mina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,求你一定要在那\NPlease be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina…\NMina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,托儿所  我希望我从没做过那种事\Nnursey, I would never do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你  - 你真是个淘气的孩子！\N- Thank you. - You're a naughty, naughty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到了你的消息\NI got your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,按照你的要求做\NI did as you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose？\NRose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Willy？\NWilly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸！\NDaddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我们吧！\NHelp us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,举起手来\NUp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\NWhat's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子呢？\NWhere are my children?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要慌  你们会很快团聚的\NDo not worry. You will be reunited soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,过去\NMove.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快走！\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在这就行  这距离够了\NRight there. That's far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一动也别动Browning先生\NKeep perfectly still, Mr. Browning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我就打死你\Nor I will shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我带来了钱  都在这\NI brought your money. It's all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道\NYes, I'm sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你不认识我了吗？\NDo you not recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该认识你吗？\NShould I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Abraham van Helsing\NAbraham van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了我全家人\NYou slaughtered my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这很难缩小范围  是么？\NThat hardly narrows it down, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个怪物\NYou are a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,比之前我\NMore vile than the one I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,释放你和你兄弟还卑鄙\Nhave unleashed upon you and your brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dracula\NDracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\NDaddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天啊！\NOh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你个混账东西  你会遭报应的！\NYou bastard. You will pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等着…\NWait...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什…你个疯子！\NWha... you madman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子呢？\NWhere are my children?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很好Browning先生\NThey're all right, Mr. Browning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在底下等着你呢\NThey're down there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只是有点害羞\NThey're just a little shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose？\NRose?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose  出来  宝贝\NRose, come out, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是我  爸爸\NIt's me, it's daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  感谢上帝\NOh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  宝贝Rose\NOh, dear Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥哥呢？\NWhere's your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这呢  爸爸\NHere, daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  William  对不起\NOh, William, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很痒\NIt itches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来  来我这\NCome. Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来爸爸这里\NCome to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.85,0:23:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊\NNo. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我用Dracula的血喂了你的孩子\NI fed your children Dracula's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们可以尽情享用你拉\NNow they can feed on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢了  先生\NOh, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina\NMina!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.61,0:24:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Alexander Grayson\NI'm Alexander Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.09,0:24:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信到现在为止\NI'm sure by now some of you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.76,0:24:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经注意到台阶上的电子设备了\Nhave noticed the electrical devices on the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.76,0:24:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外  我们在外面也安装了这些设备\Nas well as those we have
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.16,0:25:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,整个区域到处都是\Ninstalled outside and throughout the district.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.87,0:25:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们从不问问自己\NSome of you no doubt have asked yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.74,0:25:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么把全部设备\Nhow did they wire all these devices
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.47,0:25:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,用一天就全接上线了\Nin one single day?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.97,0:25:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,答案出奇地简单\NThe answer is as astonishing as it is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.74,0:25:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们根本不需要用到电线\NThey need no wires...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.27,0:25:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们马上看到的突破成果\NFor the breakthrough you are about to see
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.67,0:25:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就是第一台无线电传播装置\Nis the first practical transmission of wireless electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.59,0:25:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Vedo Dracula.\NVedo Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.56,0:25:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我看到他了  - 在哪儿  他在哪儿啊\N- I see him. - Where? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.50,0:25:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在河边\NDown by the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.65,0:25:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,站在人群前面\NStanding before a vast crowd of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.51,0:25:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson.\NGrayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.59,0:25:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人\NSenora...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.18,0:26:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是从教皇军械处得来的另一份礼物\NAnother gift from the papal armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.69,0:26:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去码头  现在出发  快点儿\NTo the docks. Now! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.68,0:26:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,八个月前  我来到了伦敦\NEight months ago I arrived in London
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.68,0:26:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,招募世界顶尖的科学奇才\Nto engage the world's leading scientific minds,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.20,0:26:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人可以看到未来\Nmen who had a vision of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.77,0:26:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,人们像我一样  将看到理想化为现实\NMen determined, like me, to see that vision become a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.49,0:26:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为全人类造福  Mina\Nto the benefit of all mankind. Mina!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.11,0:26:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一位挚友\NA dear friend of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.39,0:26:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她说最近很欣赏我的坦诚\Nrecently told me that she admired my honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.17,0:26:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我们看看  - Mina\N- Show us! - Mina!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.71,0:26:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我们瞧瞧  - 给我们瞧瞧\N- Show us! - Show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.35,0:27:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧  瞧瞧  瞧瞧  瞧瞧\NShow us, show us, show us, show us, show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.41,0:27:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina  咱们得快离开这\NMina, we have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.45,0:27:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 干嘛  - 那个共振器\N- What? - The resonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.42,0:27:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟前刚被设置为引爆状态\NFive minutes from when it's switched on it's set to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.96,0:27:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kowalski先生\NMr. Kowalski.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.46,0:27:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,第一步\NStage one...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.40,0:27:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,启动\NMark.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.35,0:27:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了\NWhat have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.09,0:27:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们看看  给我们看看  给我们看看...\NShow us, show us, show us, show us...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.77,0:27:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间说了\NThere's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.71,0:27:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-走开  别挡道 - 别推我\N- Move! Out of my way! - Don't push me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.28,0:27:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,第二步  启动！\NStage two... Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.93,0:27:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来  快停止演示\NStop! Stop the demonstration!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.00,0:27:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有人动过手脚\NIt's been sabotaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.28,0:27:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这台机器被动过手脚了\NThe machine has been sabotaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你得把它关掉\NYou have to shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.19,0:28:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谁动的手脚\NSabotaged by who?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.97,0:28:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚  Jonathan刚告诉我的\NI don't know. Jonathan's just told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.28,0:28:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker.\NHarker.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.58,0:28:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,把它关掉\NShut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.92,0:28:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没反应！\NShe's not responding!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.83,0:28:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.02,0:28:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina  我们快离开这\NMina, we have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.42,0:28:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我\NDon't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.19,0:28:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你做了什么\NWhat did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.77,0:28:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你做了什么\NWhat did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.29,0:28:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那台发电机\NThe generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.26,0:28:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把线绕过来\NWe reversed the wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.36,0:28:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快带她离开这\NGet her out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.39,0:29:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina  跟着Harker走！\NMina! Go with Harker!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.47,0:29:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  - 跟着Harker走\N- No. - Go with Harker!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.70,0:29:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  不  不\NNo, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.90,0:29:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,马上带所有人离开这\NGet everyone out of here right now
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要爆炸了\Nbefore the place explodes!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.30,0:29:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快  大家快跑\NCome on! Everybody out!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.77,0:29:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快走  走  - Alexander\N- Get out of here! Move! - Alexander!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.45,0:29:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander\NAlexander!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.65,0:29:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.63,0:29:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  保持冷静\NThat's it, stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.73,0:30:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander  Alexander\NAlexander? Alexander!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.83,0:30:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他已经死了   - 不\N- He's dead. - No...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.42,0:30:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他死了  - 不\N- He's dead. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.62,0:30:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不可能活着  - 不  这不可能\N- He wouldn't have survived. - No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.79,0:30:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina\NMina.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.14,0:30:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个杀人犯\NYou're a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.37,0:30:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是你杀了他和这些无辜的人\NYou murdered him and all these innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.19,0:31:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Szabo\NSzabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.51,0:31:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Szabo\NSzabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.28,0:31:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.57,0:32:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson\NGrayson!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.96,0:32:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson  你个混蛋\NGrayson, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.51,0:32:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你还活着\NI know you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.75,0:33:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  Jayne\NHello, Jayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.96,0:33:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道你是谁  - 你从心底\N- I know who you are. - You've always known.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.86,0:33:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都知道\NDeep down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.68,0:33:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,承认吧\NAdmit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.70,0:33:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 Jayne\NWalk away, Jayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.26,0:33:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,离开我\NFrom me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.63,0:33:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,离开他们\NFrom them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.61,0:33:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好好活着\NLive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.81,0:33:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,生命是宝贵的\NLife is precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.16,0:33:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.86,0:34:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,居然用枪\NGuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.57,0:34:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才像话\NThat's more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.86,0:34:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你爱我\NI thought you loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.17,0:34:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我骗你的\NI lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.32,0:35:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对不住了  Jayne\NSorry, Jayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.56,0:35:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你这些玩意儿对我都不管用\NI've grown immune to all your toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.12,0:35:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解你的内心\NI know what's inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.31,0:35:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗\NThe darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.33,0:35:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我生活在黑暗中\NI live in the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.32,0:35:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我渴望光明\NBut I yearn for the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.35,0:35:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,即使受伤\Neven though it burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.52,0:35:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要那样的生活\NI want life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.22,0:36:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为你能躲过Mina Murray这个劫吗\NAnd you think that you can live through Mina Murray?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.40,0:36:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你从来都不是她想要的人\NYou can never be what she needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.64,0:36:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你个不死的怪物\NYou undead thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.86,0:36:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了我吧\NKill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.34,0:36:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别把我变成吸血鬼\NDon't turn me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.15,0:36:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠我的\NYou owe me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.94,0:37:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMother?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.88,0:37:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妈\NMama...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.03,0:37:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈  来这儿  亲亲我\NCome to me, mother. Kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.86,0:37:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy  我很担心你\NLucy, I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.53,0:37:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,抱着我  妈妈 抱着我\NHold me, mama. Hold me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.80,0:38:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我的宝贝\NOh, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.09,0:38:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我以为我永远失去你了\NOh, I thought I had lost you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.98,0:38:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander\NAlexander?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.76,0:38:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander\NAlexander?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.19,0:39:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina\NMina.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.39,0:39:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aleander\NAlexander.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.04,0:39:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我好害怕我就这么失去你了\NI was so afraid that I had lost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.04,0:39:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这儿\NI'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.42,0:39:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在这儿\NI'll always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.29,0:39:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ilona\NIlona.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.45,0:39:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,从我记事起\NShe's someone I've always loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.11,0:39:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是我的挚爱\Nas long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.41,0:39:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 从过去就是 - 嗯\N- From a past life? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.86,0:39:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,从过去就是\NFrom a past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.60,0:39:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,直到此时此刻\NAnd here, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.72,0:39:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样\NBut how?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.14,0:39:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.81,0:39:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,从第一次见到你\NI've asked myself that same
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.65,0:40:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也问过自己这个问题\Nquestion since first I laid my eyes on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.46,0:40:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太神奇了\NBy some miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.06,0:41:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我收到了你的信  - Harker先生\N- I got your message. - Mr. Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.32,0:41:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\NPlease, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.32,0:42:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,关于Grayson你知道些什么\NWhat can you tell me about Grayson?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.99,0:42:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所有足以让你毁了他的事\NEverything you need to know to destroy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.54,0:42:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字\NHis name...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.15,0:42:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是Dracula\NIs Dracula.
